                        "email": "jk@ozlabs.org",
                        "username": "jk-ozlabs"
                    },
                    "message": "We're already in this state..."
                },
                {
                    "file": "serial.c",
                    "line": 227,
                    "reviewer": {
                        "name": "Nikhil Namjoshi",
                        "email": "nikhilnamjoshi@google.com",
                        "username": "namjoshiniks"
                    },
                    "message": "Yes, but I wanted to keep this just for readability and to make it explicitly clear. I can remove it if there is strong preference. Let me know.\n\n\nAlso I wonder, why did the OpenBMC CI tool did not kick in for the review ? Can you add it in the CL ? I don't seem to have permission"
                },
